.TH uiSetTool  22.14 "Fri Oct 06 02:12:27 2023" 
.SH Name \fBuiSetTool\fR \-  Selects specified tool widget in the main window and enters interactive mode
.SH Syntax \fBuiSetTool\fR  [-help]  <mode> 
.P Selects specified tool widget in the main window and enters interactive mode.
.P For more information on tool widgets, see the "Tool Widgets" section in the The Main Window chapter of the Innovus Menu Reference. 
.SH Parameters   "\fB-help\fR" Prints a brief description that includes type and default information for each uiSetTool parameter.  For a detailed description of the command and all of its parameters, use the man command:   man uiSetTool.  "\fB<mode> {select | move | ruler | util | cut | obstruct | layerBlk | ptnFeed | ptnPinBlk | ptnPinGuide | addWire | addVia | cutWire | stretchWire | addPoly | addBusGuide | p2pRoute}\fR" Specifies the interactive mode to enter. The following modes are supported:
.RS  "*" 2 select - Chooses the Select tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 move - Selects the Move/Resize/Reshape tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 ruler - Selects the Create Ruler tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 util - Selects the Query Area Density tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 cut - Selects the Cut Rectilinear tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 obstruct - Selects the Create Placement Blockage widget in the main window.  "*" 2 layerBlk - Selects the Create Routing Blockage tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 ptnFeed - Selects the Create Physical Feedthrough tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 ptnPinBlk - Selects the Create Pin Blockage tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 ptnPinGuide - Selects the Create Pin Guide tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 addWire - Selects the Edit Wire tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 addVia - Selects the Add Via tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 cutWire - Selects the Cut Wire tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 stretchWire - Selects the Move/Resize Wire tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 addPoly - Selects the Add Polygon tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 addBusGuide - Selects the Edit Bus Guide tool widget in the main window.  "*" 2 p2pRoute - Selects the Point to Point Route tool widget in the main window.
.RE 
.SH Example
.P The following command is used to enter the Create Ruler mode in the design window.
.P uiSetTool ruler 
.SH Related Information
.RS  "*" 2 The Main Window chapter of the Menu Reference 
.RS  "*" 2 Tool Widgets
.RE 
.RE
.P
